      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，feature分支从初始提交a切出来。那feature分支的显示顺序需要调整吗？默认可能会和main重叠。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch feature",
        "order"
